{"tid":545586,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩中國主教遭梵蒂岡「迫宮」   陳日君網誌疑遭河蟹","createTime":"2018-01-30T15:58:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T16:37:49.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d181ff29744795b289287bbe0047566cbd8f10bb","tid":545586,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T15:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180130/large/1517325589_5ae7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180130%2Flarge%2F1517325589_5ae7.png&h=022d379d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n教廷發言人於羅馬時間周二下午罕有發表聲明，不點名批評天主教香港教區榮休主教陳日君樞機的言論製造混亂和爭議。<br />\n<br />\n陳周一發表網誌，確認教內傳言，指梵蒂岡要求兩名中國主教辭職，讓位予中共承認的人選；他月初就此事親往梵蒂岡向教宗陳情，引述教宗指不會讓「迫宮」事件在中國發生，行文多次暗示教廷中人阻礙教宗得知中國教會真相。<br />\n<br />\n教廷發言人指，教宗與國務卿在中國事務上有恆常聯繫，了解中國教會的情況，對於教會中人提出相反言論感意外及遺憾。陳日君網誌現時未能連上，未知是否被關閉。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180130/large/1517325742_21dc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180130%2Flarge%2F1517325742_21dc.png&h=31afd236&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳日君在網誌中多次暗示教廷中人阻礙教宗得知中國教會真相。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180130/large/1517325673_2faa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180130%2Flarge%2F1517325673_2faa.png&h=7ad92a83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳日君的網誌到周二晚上已無法登入。"},{"pid":"e295a357509352fa5fd8934752638ad3f69aaa40","tid":545586,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:00:27.000Z","msg":"教宗應該知真相啦<br />\n<br />\n教庭黑暗都唔係今日既事<br />\n<br />\n泛民又將「支那國家主席係好精明係好人、身邊官員暪香港真相」既自我FF套去梵蒂岡"},{"pid":"f1ce231cbb6727e0f4f833d04ca2e9f2cb25159d","tid":545586,"uid":550,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:03:41.000Z","msg":"呢鋪陳日君好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但教廷仲黑暗過達文西密碼<br />\n教宗只係權力下嘅兒皇帝"},{"pid":"6d428077a6e4a4f25f929726f8fb8f7206f40fff","tid":545586,"uid":13663,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:04:54.000Z","msg":"陳日君先應該做教宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035cc049a0188931009f13eceeea2bb85826815f","tid":545586,"uid":19501,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:07:46.000Z","msg":"陳日君<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836e1b9299beb7d72ab08b5e45a73db4bd9f1be2","tid":545586,"uid":58335,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:10:09.000Z","msg":"天主教學人講正義真係好好笑<br />\n咁好就唔會分裂出基督教同東正教啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同個無神論既國家做交易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104256a5a8b9a80957f65149ee55b807bf99924a","tid":545586,"uid":53577,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:14:05.000Z","msg":"梵蒂岡先係antichrist, 一直都係撒旦無間道。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d89220bd40151e061d1eaeb2f1655f2e6be25a","tid":545586,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:17:20.000Z","msg":"陳日君真係最好果個"},{"pid":"2d75f8a1820248f7373dbe485c4ca09b3510f9b6","tid":545586,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:21:14.000Z","msg":"唔鐘意咪另自己立新教囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfdae35a6ffd00802e751070a3a0fd3c023ef2a2","tid":54